\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gqe1665702707701.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gqe1665702707701.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gqe1665702707701.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gqe1665702707701\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the profiling format.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__topic_d142505e1_d142506e1_d142507e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__p_d142508e1_d142509e1_d142510e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SeparatorCode</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__section_vzc_blv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479611e64\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__p_d142514e1_d142515e1_d142516e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SeparatorCode</var>—one of:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__ul_g2k_clv_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__li_d50123e1_d50124e1_d50125e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Gold</code>—a Uniface separator, that\n               is, GOLD semicolon ( <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>\n</code> ); default </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__li_d50126e1_d50127e1_d50128e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Tab</code>—a Tab character </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__li_d50129e1_d50130e1_d50131e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Comma</code>—a comma\n                  (<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__li_d50132e1_d50133e1_d50134e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Semicolon</code>—a semicolon\n                  (<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code>) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__section_jd4_dlv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479611e110\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__table_d17126e1_d17127e1_d17128e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">client assignment files</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Gold</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__section_i4g_glv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479611e158\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__p_d142523e1_d142524e1_d142525e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR</span>\n            determines which separator is used to separate the items in the profiling information.\n            You can define a separator for use outside of Uniface.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__p_d142526e1_d142527e1_d142528e1\">The default separator is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Gold</code> ( <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>\n</code>).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__section_cmq_jlv_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d479611e181\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR</code></h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__p_d142532e1_d142533e1_d142534e1\">In this example, you define a comma to separate the\n            profiling information.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"gqe1665702707701__pre_uvq_klv_jwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR=comma</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527967\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527967\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the profiling format. $PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR = SeparatorCode Arguments SeparatorCode —one of: Gold —a Uniface separator, that is, GOLD semicolon ( ; ); default Tab —a Tab character Comma —a comma ( , ) Semicolon —a semicolon ( ; ) Defaults Assignment file: client assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: Gold Description $PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR determines which separator is used to separate the items in the profiling information. You can define a separator for use outside of Uniface. The default separator is Gold ( ; ). Example: $PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR In this example, you define a comma to separate the profiling information. $PROC_PROFILING_SEPARATOR=comma Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}